t 4. mai 1982 at det gjøres følgende endring i ovennevnte forskrift:</article> <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">§ 3 nr. 2 skal lyde:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">2.</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Ved behandling og kontroll hos lege for tuberkulose.</article></article></li></ul></article><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/ledd/2/" id="ledd-2">Endringen trer i kraft straks.</article></main></body></html>